import React from 'react';

import './estilo.css';
import { Button, TextField } from '@material-ui/core';
function DadosEntrega() {
    return (
        <form id="teste">
            <TextField 
                sx={{
                    width: '49.5%',  
                    padding: '0.08em',
                }}
                id="cep"
                label="CEP"
                type="number"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
            />

            <TextField
            sx={{
                width: '49.5%',  
                padding: '0.08em',
            }}
                id="numero"
                label="Número"
                type="number"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
            />

            <TextField
                id="endereco"
                label="Endereço"
                type="text"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                fullWidth
            />

            <TextField
                id="estado"
                label="Estado"
                type="text"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
            />
            <TextField
                id="cidade"
                label="Cidade"
                type="text"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
            />

            <Button
                variant="contained"
                color="primary"
                type="submit"
                fullWidth>
                Cadastrar
            </Button>

        </form>
    )
}

export default DadosEntrega;
